book.part:
Using jEdit



   This part of the user's guide covers jEdit's text editing commands, along
   with basic usage of macros and plugins. Information and developing macros and
   plugins can be found in subsequent parts of the user's guide.




   This part of the user's guide was written by Slava Pestov
   (slava@jedit.org).



